{"tid":1883073,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[入市啦] 戴口罩排隊睇樓 買家開始心急","createTime":"2020-02-16T16:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T10:48:10.000Z","uid":275872,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0f17feecb5af2386cea4edf63f7ad9d05d0409d3","tid":1883073,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:41:18.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=ddb9e897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】雖然疫情肆虐，但二手買家依然趁低爭相入市「肺炎盤」，市場氣氛稍為回升，<span style=\"color: red;\">部分屋苑再出現戴口罩排隊睇樓情況</span>！利嘉閣溫錦駒表示，將軍澳周六(15日)單日錄行逾10宗二手買賣，盤源被迅速消化，準<span style=\"color: red;\">買家開始心急</span>。<br />\n<br />\n其中，新寶城5座一個低層兩房單位，業主願意開門睇樓，開價亦由早前的650萬元，減至606萬元，屬屋苑入場單位，即引來睇樓客輪候參觀，更曾有4至5組客、共<span style=\"color: red;\">逾10多人於走廊排隊，等候業主開門。</span><br />\n<br />\n溫氏續稱，該盤本月已錄至少4宗買賣，其中1座高層H室，實用面積644方呎，剛售952萬元，呎價14,783元。<br />\n<br />\n此外，同區指標新都城錄本月首宗二手買賣。市場消息稱，項目1期1座高層單位，實用面積364方呎，曾叫價650萬元，其後減至630萬元。單位亦有排隊睇樓人龍，市傳已售約620萬元，呎價17,033元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://yns.page.link/SErba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyns.page.link%2FSErba&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=09262c81\" target=\"_blank\">https://yns.page.link/SErba</a>"},{"pid":"3dfbd3bb612a34b673f48bb095a8f7c9701d3198","tid":1883073,"uid":275872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"it's time!!!!"},{"pid":"0767c0e32aea565862bd7cdf83f8c730eed3c19f","tid":1883073,"uid":275872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"嘈嘈地發達!!!"},{"pid":"e950d74438ef0af5ae233c116a82c0c1e206f6c9","tid":1883073,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T18:33:34.000Z","msg":"迎接私有財產公有制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c74ed50dcbce0c227091a99631634aa419689a","tid":18830